title: Co-Hashtag Network Showing Hashtags Associated with Amazon Fires
description: Twitter data collected with TCAT tool from 24th August to 2nd September 2019 using hashtags: ActForTheAmazon, amazonfires, AmazonRainforest, PrayforAmazonia, SaveTheAmazon, SOSAmazonia.
